OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1781614113
OL,3,CEden Festival: Music returns to Moffat
OL,4,Cfor the 15th year
OL,6,FThousands of people are expected to
OL,7,Fattend an independent volunteer-run
OL,8,Ffestival near Moffat this weekend, as
OL,9,Fit marks 15 years of live music.
OL,11,FThe Eden festival will see more than
OL,12,F250 acts perform, across 10 stages,
OL,13,Fand runs from Thursday (11 June) until
OL,14,FSunday (14 June).
OL,16,FStephen Scott's band, Have Mercy Las
OL,17,FVegas, is performing on the Rabbies
OL,18,FTavern stage this weekend, as Scotland
OL,19,Ftake to the pitch in the World Cup for
OL,20,Fthe first time in 28 years.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
