PN,32802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1781614113
OL,3,CEden Festival: Music returns to Moffat
OL,4,Cfor the 15th year
OL,6,FHe says it was the first stage the
OL,7,Fband performed on and have since gone
OL,8,Fon to perform at gigs across Scotland
OL,9,Fand internationally.
OL,11,FSpeaking about the importance of
OL,12,Fsmaller festivals, he said: "I think
OL,13,Fit's vital. I think sadly so many
OL,14,Ffestivals are falling by the way side.
OL,15,FBands are finding it harder to get
OL,16,Fbooked because the pond is so shallow
OL,17,Fnow.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1781614113
OL,3,CEden Festival: Music returns to Moffat
OL,4,Cfor the 15th year
OL,6,F"It's vital for bands to get a chance
OL,7,Fto play on a decent stage and then
OL,8,Fmaybe the next year go onto a bigger
OL,9,Fstage. Hopefully these wee festivals,
OL,10,Fwhich maybe do a better job at
OL,11,Fsupporting the smaller acts, continue
OL,12,Fto flourish."
OL,14,FChris Blackmore, one of the
OL,15,Fprogrammers for the Eden Festival
OL,16,Fsaid: "It's grown quite a lot,
OL,17,Fevolved, new stages, different ideas,
OL,18,Fit's like an evolving community
OL,19,Fproject.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
