FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1781614113
OL,3,CEden Festival: Music returns to Moffat
OL,4,Cfor the 15th year
OL,6,F"We've got over 250 bands across ten
OL,7,Fdifferent stages, Julian Marly
OL,8,Fheadlining, drum and base, dance,
OL,9,Ftechno, it's family friendly too so we
OL,10,Fhave lots for the kids to do."
OL,12,FThe build of the festival takes a
OL,13,Fcouple of weeks.
OL,15,FChris aded: "You definitely see the
OL,16,Fbenefits for the local economy and
OL,17,Fcommunity, folk get involved as well,
OL,18,Fthis doesn't happen without the blood,
OL,19,Fsweat and tears of locals volunteering
OL,20,Fcoming together to create this."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/4
